findings.title: Owner can mint any amounts of tokens
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to mint unlimited amounts of tokens without restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can update _startTime and _restrictionLiftTime
findings.description: The owner has privileges to update _startTime and _restrictionLiftTime variables.

findings.title: Owner can set max restriction amount
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to set the maximum restriction amount.

findings.title: Owner can change gas restrictions
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to modify gas restrictions.

findings.title: Owner can blacklist accounts
findings.description: The owner has the privilege to blacklist accounts without any restrictions.
